long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Native Client is an open-source technology for running native compiled code in the browser, with the goal of maintaining the OS portability and safety that people expect from web apps.

This application demonstrates the examples that are included with the Native Client SDK.

To Download the SDK, or learn more about Native Client, please refer to http://developers.google.com/native-client
